Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: Really nice place, good and moderate priced cocktails, live music. A bohemian and different place in Amsterdam with nice people

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: My favourite music venue in Amsterdam, great bar, beautiful vibes, friendly people and incredible music nights of local bands. Drink prices are good tooo! I love it here!

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: This hidden gem in Amsterdam is a locals best kept secret bar & party place. I loved the venue and the vibe. The drinks are competitively priced so you'd enjoy your night drinking. …

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: Good drinks and nice stage for dance freaks like me :)

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: an alternative place in which you can dance rock n roll or swing and enjoy nice coctails. It is very hot inside, so be sure you come with a t shirt

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: Post alternative place. Nice and not posh. cheap drinks and nice music (yesterday new wave, in general it changes a lot as music style). suggested.

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: Nice atmosphere, cool crowd, great cocktails, often good music.

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: lovely place, friendly staff, and amazing events:)

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: Cool alternative place. Warm and cozy. Nice atmosphere, good vibes and fair prices. They usually feature live music, and host many kinds of events, which it makes an interesting place to visit also during the week days. I like their vintage decoration, friendly staff and tasty cocktails.

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: A new love affair for me. This place is marvellous. The beers, the characters, the atmosphere. It’s just so fantastically weird. It’s certainly worth checking out the agenda for upcoming events as there’s something for everyone with an interest in the unusual. It’s like the living room I wish I had.

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: Great place, great music, great people :)

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: Vintage decoration and awesome atmosphere, with friendly staff and tasty cocktails. They usually feature live music, and host many kinds of events - all in all: great place!

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text:
The focus here is on the music and drinks, not on being modern or chic.
In that way it is refreshing change in Amsterdam. Great mixed drinks. Also a very intimate and unique venue.

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: This place was awesome. Everything from the decorations, furniture and music was amazing. Disco, boogie and soul. We were dancing and having a fantastic time. Highly recommend this place!

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: I used to live in the area and frequented it every Tuesday night for live music: 2 EUR entry and great musicians from a variety of genres.  Definitely one of my favourite cafés in Amsterdam

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: Cool bar / music venue, very hip. Reminds me of bars in Berlin. Friendly place, plays good music. I try to make a stop there every time I visit Amsterdam.

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: Always 5 stars for this place

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: Cosy, Great vibe and very good cocktails. They host poetry nights, live music and dance nights. No big bouncers, good tunes and fair prices

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: I saw the cutest girl EVER there. I was nervous to talk to her first but she was sooooo sweet. Best place ever! Beer could be a bit cheaper tho.

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: One of my favorite places in Amsterdam! Not just a lovely bar, but basically a cultural center with many awesome events and concerts!

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: Awesome cocktails! Two different dance floors with DJs belting out nostalgic tunes. On Saturday, I saunteredbfrom the '50s into the '70s.

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text:
Niewe anita is a one-of-a-kind place.
The great ambiance, the stellar drinks on Saturdays and the laid back artsy atmosphere make this venue unique and worth visiting every time.

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: I like the venue, a bit punk and and scruffy but cool, I am a bit annoyed since last time they asked me to pay since there was a gig inside, but when I got in I realised the gig was finished already...not nice

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: Great little classic Amsterdam bar. Super friendly staff, a really decent beer selection and live music all the time.

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: It is a very nice bar, nice people welcome you. There is also a scene for theater or concerts. Very nice place to discover absolutely!

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: Fantastic place. Lot of local cool peeps, great dancing floor and old school alure all around@

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: Nice old house style bar with comfy chair and sofa's, downstairs they have a small stage where I enjoyed the Trouble notes it's a cosy place.

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text:
Perfect night out.
When you enter you'l see a living room with vintage chairs and couches, but when there is live music, you can walk to the back and a whole new world opens here.

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: Experience the Dutch cozyness in a bar with a lot of nice open people, plus a "secret" passage way into Robin food for a great vegan dinner.

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: Fantastic movies are played every Monday!!! Check the FB page for the up-to-date schedule.

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
Review Text: Cool place, chill music and extremely nice staff. If you're lucky enough, you might get a free beer on the house!

Name: De Nieuwe Anita

Name: De Nieuwe Anita
